column5: Hope you enjoy this as much as we did when she caught it, we spent 30 minutes reviving it & it swam away very strong Richard    http://south-bruce-guide-service.blogspot.com/
Good for Jenna.  And from a canoe as well.  Must have been a fun ride.
Thick.. I caught my biggest, 47", from a canoe as well, fun stuff.
What an awesome fish, she must have been thrilled.
wowzers!!! That's a nice thick fish, too!
Awesome ski Richard   Congratulations to Jenna Thanks for sharing Leechman
